How would you describe acessibility on the web to someone new to programming?

Acessibility on the web essentialy means how easy a website easy to navigate for everyone, even those with disablities.

Talk about 3 different things you can do to ensure your website is accessible.

Using responsive design helps people with every type of device be able to access your website, using photo's high in contrast help people with
color blindness see images, you can also provide text alternatives for people that are hard of seeing or blind.

How would you explain the concept of a variable to someone new to programming?
A variable is simple a reference to a specific piece of data in your program. A variable is useful because it allows us to keep track of certain pieces of data.

What is the purpose of using functions in code?
Functions are very useful because they allow us to shorten up code operations. Using functions is a huge time savor and adds complexity to your programs.